1
00:00:49,700 --> 00:00:51,450
There is nothing to choose from.

2
00:00:51,450 --> 00:00:54,250
My fate, Xie Jingchen, is never decided by others.

3
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,600
Protecting you and guarding this city gate

4
00:00:57,830 --> 00:00:59,370
is the path I chose myself.

5
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:04,120
Villains, ten years of blood debts.

6
00:01:04,540 --> 00:01:07,540
Today I want you to pay for it with your lives!

7
00:01:11,250 --> 00:01:12,660
Is that all you've got?

8
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:15,730
Your father was much stronger than you back then.

9
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:23,830
Sister, you can protect him for a while,

10
00:01:23,830 --> 00:01:25,200
but can you protect him for a lifetime?

11
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,700
You will soon know

12
00:01:26,789 --> 00:01:28,539
why you reincarnate again and again

13
00:01:28,539 --> 00:01:30,330
and forget yourself again and again.

14
00:01:30,330 --> 00:01:33,039
You can never break this curse.

15
00:01:42,450 --> 00:01:43,410
It's all right.

16
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:49,039
The allocation of provisions must be confirmed again and again.

17
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:51,830
We must be on guard against the remnants of the Xiongnu.

18
00:01:51,830 --> 00:01:53,039
Border defense matters,

19
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:54,330
no matter how big or small,

20
00:01:54,330 --> 00:01:55,990
must be handled with caution.

21
00:01:56,580 --> 00:01:57,370
Yes.

22
00:02:01,660 --> 00:02:03,620
The border defense has been arranged properly.

23
00:02:03,620 --> 00:02:05,160
We set off to return to the capital.

24
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:07,000
First, to investigate and deal with the remnants of treacherous ministers,

25
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09,120
and give an explanation to the families of the 300 loyal souls.

26
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,699
Second, the history museum in the capital,

27
00:02:10,699 --> 00:02:11,830
the royal library,

28
00:02:11,950 --> 00:02:14,750
may contain records of Lady Dudeng from a hundred years ago.

29
00:02:14,750 --> 00:02:17,010
I will accompany you to find your answer.

30
00:02:18,450 --> 00:02:19,579
General, no.

31
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:21,040
The road ahead is completely blocked.

32
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:23,000
This section of the official road is already leaning against the mountain wall.

33
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,620
The flash flood washed it away and collapsed.

34
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:26,040
It blocked a full three to four miles of road.

35
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:27,540
Even if our people can clear it,

36
00:02:27,540 --> 00:02:29,870
it won't be cleared for three to five days.

37
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,579
There is no other way to bypass.

38
00:02:31,579 --> 00:02:34,370
There is, but we have to go around the mountain col next to it.

39
00:02:34,370 --> 00:02:35,579
Take that mountain path,

40
00:02:35,579 --> 00:02:36,950
pass through Luoxia Village at the foot of the mountain,

41
00:02:36,950 --> 00:02:38,000
take an extra 20 miles,

42
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,450
and then you can get back to the official road ahead.

43
00:02:39,450 --> 00:02:41,950
It's just that Luoxia Village is very evil.

44
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,450
There is a mountain god enshrined in the mountains.

45
00:02:43,450 --> 00:02:44,790
Sacrifices are made every year,

46
00:02:44,790 --> 00:02:45,829
and the rules are very strict.

47
00:02:45,829 --> 00:02:48,790
We people who are traveling generally don't dare to mess with it.

48
00:02:48,790 --> 00:02:50,450
The life-and-death road is blocked.

49
00:02:50,450 --> 00:02:51,579
Who cares about the rules?

50
00:02:51,579 --> 00:02:53,440
Change course to Luoxia Village.

51
00:02:56,950 --> 00:02:59,329
A'Deng, this village sounds evil.

52
00:02:59,329 --> 00:03:00,250
Are you afraid?

53
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,460
Mountain God's blessing,

54
00:03:15,830 --> 00:03:17,329
sacrifice and send girls.

55
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:19,210
Mountain God's blessing,

56
00:03:19,579 --> 00:03:21,040
sacrifice and send girls.

57
00:03:21,660 --> 00:03:23,120
Mountain God's blessing,

58
00:03:23,410 --> 00:03:24,870
sacrifice and send girls.

59
00:03:31,250 --> 00:03:32,160
Stop it.

60
00:03:44,540 --> 00:03:45,410
Are you crazy?

61
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:46,700
A living girl,

62
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:47,829
you just send her to the mountain like this.

63
00:03:47,829 --> 00:03:48,750
This is murder.

64
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,329
What do outsiders know?

65
00:03:51,329 --> 00:03:53,530
This is the rule set by the Mountain God.

66
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,620
More than a dozen people died,

67
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:57,120
just because they didn't sacrifice on time

68
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,750
and angered the Mountain God.

69
00:03:58,750 --> 00:04:01,000
If we don't send virgins to the mountain this year,

70
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,410
the Mountain God will punish us,

71
00:04:02,410 --> 00:04:04,450
and our whole village will die.

72
00:04:15,450 --> 00:04:18,050
This is not the Mountain God, it's resentment.

73
00:04:18,250 --> 00:04:21,329
You are all covered with evil spirits.

74
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:25,790
You don't worship the mountain god at all,

75
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:28,960
but an evil spirit nourished by human sacrifices.

76
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,909
I am Xie Jingchen, General Dingyuan of the current dynasty.

77
00:04:32,909 --> 00:04:36,159
Living human sacrifice is a capital crime intolerable by national law.

78
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:38,330
I will take care of this matter today.

79
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,370
Guard the village well

80
00:04:44,370 --> 00:04:45,580
and keep an eye on this girl.

81
00:04:45,580 --> 00:04:47,330
Miss Adeng and I will go into the mountain

82
00:04:47,330 --> 00:04:49,159
to see what this mountain god of yours

83
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,409
really is.

84
00:04:51,370 --> 00:04:52,790
I'll go with you.

85
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:54,830
There might be injured people in the mountain.

86
00:04:54,830 --> 00:04:56,700
If evil spirits hurt anyone, I can provide medical aid.

87
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:58,250
An extra pair of hands will help.

88
00:04:58,250 --> 00:04:59,200
You stay here.

89
00:04:59,330 --> 00:05:02,130
The villagers and this girl need your protection.

90
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,330
Ying is full of tricks.

91
00:05:03,330 --> 00:05:05,250
I'm afraid this is a scheme to lure us away.

92
00:05:05,250 --> 00:05:06,950
I feel at ease with you here.

93
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:14,450
You stay in the village

94
00:05:14,450 --> 00:05:16,750
and guard Miss Qinghe and the villagers closely.

95
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:17,790
If there's any unusual movement,

96
00:05:17,790 --> 00:05:18,790
fire a signal arrow immediately.

97
00:05:18,790 --> 00:05:19,580
Do not fail.

98
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:20,750
Yes, General.

99
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:40,159
This resentment is exactly the same as Ying's.

100
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:41,820
It's not just her resentment.

101
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:44,159
It's also mixed with the aura of living souls.

102
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:46,290
More than one child has been murdered.

103
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,159
Wait for me at the cave entrance.

104
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:54,370
The resentment inside is too heavy.

105
00:05:54,370 --> 00:05:55,250
I'm afraid you'll get hurt.

106
00:05:55,250 --> 00:05:56,180
I'll go with you.

107
00:05:56,950 --> 00:05:58,790
I said that wherever you go,

108
00:05:58,790 --> 00:05:59,830
I will be with you.

109
00:06:24,330 --> 00:06:25,120
Ah!

110
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,909
Hahaha.

111
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,950
Sister, you're finally here.

112
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,620
I've been waiting for you for a long time.
